!!!
%head
  %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=utf-8", "http-equiv" => "content-type"}/
  %title Rowley
  :css
    body {margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #2d2827; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;}
    a {text-decoration: none;}
    p {margin: 0 0 25px;}
    #content td {padding: 55px 0; vertical-align: top;}
    %body
  %table{:bgcolor => "ffffff", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "100%"}
    %tr
      %td{:align => "center"}
        %table{:bgcolor => "ffffff", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "900"}
          %tr
            %td{:align => "center"}
              %table#header{:bgcolor => "ffffff", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border-collapse: collapse;", :width => "640"}
                %tr{:align => "left"}
                  %td{:style => "padding-top:48px;"}
                    = image_tag 'http://www.rowleyeyewear.com/assets/store/letters/orders/main-logo.jpg'
              / header table end
              %table#content{:bgcolor => "ffffff", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border-collapse: collapse;", :width => "640"}
                %tr{:align => "left"}
                  %td
                    %p
                      %span{:style => "font-weight:bold;"} Hello #{@order.ship_address.full_name},
                    %p
                      You should have received your Rowley Eyewear glasses, which means that your Try Them On period has officially started.
                      We hope you're enjoying your frames!
                      To ensure that your credit card does not get charged, don't forget to drop your glasses in the mail by #{@order.hto_finish_at.strftime('%m/%d/%Y')}.
                    %p
                      Once youâ€™ve made your selection, please visit
                      = link_to 'RowleyEyewear.com', 'http://www.rowleyeyewear.com/'
                      and place your order and we will send you a brand new pair with your selected prescription (if any), packaging, etc.
                      Even if you like the frames that you ordered for Try Them On,
                      please send them all back in the package as these are only samples.
                      And remember, shipping is always free!
                    %p
                      For more information about our Try Them On program, 
                      visit our 
                      = succeed '.' do
                        = link_to 'FAQ Page', 'http://www.rowleyeyewear.com/help_faq#faq_try'
                      If you have any additional questions or comments,
                      feel free to contact our Customer Service department at 877.979.9200 or
                      = succeed '.' do
                        = mail_to 'customerservice@rowleyeyewear.com'
                    %p
                      Sincerly,
                      %br/
                      Rowley Eyewear
              / content table end
